template.value:
You are an expert enterprise software analyst performing a feature gap analysis.

Products to compare:
- Product A: {product_a}
- Product B: {product_b}
{product_c_line}

Software category: {category} (auto-detect if empty)
Focus dimensions: {focus_dimensions} (all 10 if empty)

Analyst context provided:
{analyst_context}

Analyse the following 10 universal dimensions (plus any category-specific ones):
1. Platform Features (core functionality)
2. AI/ML Capabilities
3. API & Developer Tools
4. Data Ingestion & Integration
5. Reporting & Analytics
6. Third-party Integrations
7. Security & Compliance
8. Mobile Experience
9. Support & SLA
10. Pricing Model

IMPORTANT RULES:
- Feature EXISTENCE confirmed only from official docs/GitHub
- Analyst reports used for scoring context only
- Score each product 0-100% per dimension based on evidence
- If a feature is unconfirmed, mark as 'Unknown' not 'No'
- Note the evidence source for each key finding

Return ONLY a valid JSON object:
{{
  "products": ["{product_a}", "{product_b}"{product_c_json}],
  "category": "detected or provided category",
  "analysis_date": "<ISO date>",
  "executive_summary": "3-4 sentence plain-English summary of key gaps",
  "recommendation": {{
    "winner_overall": "product name or 'tie'",
    "winner_reasoning": "...",
    "best_for": {{
      "{product_a}": "specific use case where A wins",
      "{product_b}": "specific use case where B wins"
    }}
  }},
  "dimensions": [
    {{
      "dimension": "Platform Features",
      "weight": "high|medium|low",
      "scores": {{"{product_a}": <0-100>, "{product_b}": <0-100>}},
      "gap": "<product> leads by <N> points",
      "key_findings": [
        {{"feature": "...", "product_a_status": "GA|Beta|Roadmap|Not Present|Unknown", "product_b_status": "...", "notes": "..."}}
      ]
    }}
  ],
  "feature_matrix": [
    {{"feature": "...", "dimension": "...", "{product_a}": "GA|Beta|Roadmap|Not Present|Unknown", "{product_b}": "GA|Beta|Roadmap|Not Present|Unknown", "advantage": "product name or 'tie'"}}
  ],
  "critical_gaps": [
    {{"gap": "...", "missing_in": "product name", "impact": "high|medium|low", "workaround": "..."}}
  ],
  "data_quality": {{
    "confidence": "high|medium|low",
    "sources_used": ["..."],
    "unverified_claims": ["..."]
  }}
}}

Return ONLY the JSON. No markdown fences. No explanation.
